    "formula":  "let\r\n    Source = Excel.Workbook(File.Contents(\"x\")),\r\n    Sheet1 = Source{[Item=\"S\",Kind=\"Sheet\"]}[Data],\r\n    Result = Table.AddColumn(Sheet1, \"Q\", each null + [A])\r\nin\r\n    Result",
